---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="About Us — Knowledge IAS Academy" description="A distinguished e-learning platform nurturing UPSC aspirants, led by Founder & Director Mr. Ajay Sah.">
  <section class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 pt-16 lg:pt-24 pb-8">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[45%] h-[70%] bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top_right,rgba(245,166,35,0.12),transparent_70%)] -z-10"></div>
    <div data-reveal>
      <span class="chip"><span class="dot"></span>About Us</span>
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight">
        A <span class="gold-underline-animated">decade of mentorship</span> behind every aspirant.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-[var(--color-muted)] max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
        Knowledge IAS Academy is a distinguished e-learning platform dedicated to nurturing aspirants preparing for the Civil Services Examination conducted by the Union Public Service Commission (UPSC).
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 pb-20">
    <div>
      <div class="prose-readable">
        <p>
          With a clear focus on quality, accessibility, and long-term academic development, the academy aims to provide a strong intellectual foundation to students who aspire to serve the nation through the civil services.
        </p>
        <p>
          At the core of its academic offerings is the flagship <strong>FOCUS SCHOOL PROGRAMME</strong>, thoughtfully designed to address the unique needs of school-going students who dream of building a career in the civil services. Recognizing that early preparation can significantly enhance a candidate's chances of success, this programme acts as a vital stepping stone by introducing students to the core subjects and concepts required for UPSC preparation at an early stage. The course offers a well-structured and progressive curriculum, combined with comprehensive guidance, ensuring that students gradually develop both depth and clarity in their understanding.
        </p>
        <p>
          Through a dynamic blend of interactive online lectures, concept-based learning, regular assessments, and mentorship support, the <strong>FOCUS SCHOOL PROGRAMME</strong> not only strengthens subject knowledge but also cultivates essential skills such as critical thinking, analytical reasoning, and answer-writing ability. These competencies are crucial for navigating the demanding and competitive landscape of the Civil Services Examination. The programme also emphasizes consistency, discipline, and intellectual curiosity, helping students build habits that are indispensable for long-term success.
        </p>
        <p>
          Knowledge IAS Academy functions under the visionary leadership of its Founder and Director, <strong>Mr. Ajay Sah</strong>, whose experience in the domain of Civil Services Examination preparation spans over a decade. His deep understanding of the examination pattern, evolving trends, and student needs enables him to design effective learning strategies and mentorship frameworks. Over the years, he has taught a wide range of subjects at several reputed institutes across the country, including <em>GS Score, Chanakya IAS, Target UPSC,</em> and <em>Quest IAS</em>, thereby gaining extensive exposure to diverse teaching methodologies and aspirant profiles.
        </p>
        <p>
          Mr. Sah's dedication to education extends beyond classroom teaching. He has actively contributed to academic discourse by conducting seminars and webinars on Civil Services Examination-related topics at some of the country's most prestigious institutions, such as IITs, NITs, BHU, St. Stephen's College, and Hindu College. These engagements reflect his commitment to guiding and motivating young minds at various stages of their academic journey.
        </p>
        <p>
          His strong academic background and consistent involvement in the field further reinforce his credibility as a mentor. With a student-centric approach and a passion for excellence, Mr. Sah continues to inspire and guide aspiring civil servants, helping them transform their ambitions into achievements. Through Knowledge IAS Academy, he envisions creating a generation of well-informed, capable, and responsible individuals ready to contribute meaningfully to public service.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
